# Git / build context should be the Jewel AI app root (contains backend/, frontend/, deploy/).
.git
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.venv
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.production.example
**/uploads
**/*.db
**/.pytest_cache
**/coverage
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/jewel.db
docs/Modals
**/*.md
!README.md
